<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15139</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得去美罗城中央银行。”罗西想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人在那抢劫。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20806</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跑向格林老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“格林老师。”罗西说，“我刚想起来了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30066</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘校长说......嗯......想要和我谈谈。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你去吧，罗西。”格林老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西很快就飞上了天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们看！”玛拉叫道，“火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔挠挠头。“罗西去哪里了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西到了美罗城中央银行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>警车包围了大楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>银行的大门被砸破了，有浓烟从里面冒出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>街对面站着一堆人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿！”史密斯侦探叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞向侦探。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您是要存支票吗，侦探先生？”罗西笑着问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯皱着眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不好笑，火箭女孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这儿发生了抢劫！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抢劫犯还在银行里吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探点点头。“我觉得是。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您知道是谁吗？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人群中一个女人站了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是想问他是‘什么’吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西不明白。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看见那个抢劫犯了。”那个女人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他看起来像一台巨型机器！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“的确是。”一个穿西装的男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他穿着又大又重的盔甲。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看起来像是军队里的坦克！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯......”史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这肯定跟美罗城军事基地的案件有关。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142083</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“军事基地发生了什么事？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人偷走了坦克。”侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生在几天前的晚上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要出去了！”一个很粗的声音在银行里吼道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们最好都给我让开！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探举起喊话器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“银行被包围了。举着手出来吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！”那个声音笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我叫汉克坦克，我是美罗城最厉害的犯人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>谁都别想阻止我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我现在要带着所有的钱出去了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西听到银行里面传来沉重的脚步声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哐！哐！哐！大楼和街道都在震动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们四处逃散。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抢劫犯出来了！”女人尖叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208475</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快逃命啊！”男人叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208476</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“汉克坦克听上去很大。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊。”罗西点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>脚步声停住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一时间一切变得很安静。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后......哗啦！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>